{\section*{parxtipAdayx viSayAnuguNavAda deVvatA sutxti}}\label{page128}

(shirxVguruvu savxlapxhotutx dhAyxnArUDarAgidudx, naMtara aMjali baMdhadoDane - I keLakaMDa sholxVka\-gaLanunx gAna mADidaru)


